---
import { site } from "../../data/site";
import "../../styles/global.css";
import "../../styles/blog-features.css";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const withBase = (path = "") => `${base}${path.replace(/^\/+/, "")}`;
const backgroundStyle = `--background-image: url("${withBase("assets/handwriting-bg.jpg")}")`;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="Blog writing guide and frontmatter template." />
    <title>Writing Guide | {site.brand.name}</title>
  </head>
  <body style={backgroundStyle}>
    <div class="backdrop" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="soft-wash" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <main class="blog-shell panel">
      <a class="back-link" href={withBase("blog/")}>Back to blog</a>
      <header class="blog-header">
        <p>WRITING GUIDE</p>
        <h1>How to write a post</h1>
        <span>Copy this structure into a new Markdown file under <code>src/content/blog</code>.</span>
      </header>

      <section class="writing-guide-grid">
        <article class="guide-card article-body">
          <h2>Frontmatter template</h2>
          <pre><code>---
title: "文章标题"
description: "文章简介，会显示在列表和搜索里"
date: "2026-06-18"
updated: "2026-06-18"
category: "Study"
series: "Astro Website Log"
tags: ["Astro", "Blog", "Learning"]
image: "assets/example-cover.jpg"
lang: "zh-CN"
pinned: false
draft: false
---

## 第一部分

正文内容。

> [!NOTE]
> 这是一个提示框。

```js
console.log("代码块可以复制");
```
</code></pre>
        </article>

        <article class="guide-card article-body">
          <h2>Fields</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><code>title</code>: 文章标题，必填。</li>
            <li><code>description</code>: 摘要，必填。</li>
            <li><code>date</code>: 发布时间，必填。</li>
            <li><code>updated</code>: 更新时间，可选。</li>
            <li><code>category</code>: 分类，不写会归到 General。</li>
            <li><code>series</code>: 系列文章名，可选。适合写多篇连续教程。</li>
            <li><code>tags</code>: 标签列表。</li>
            <li><code>image</code>: 封面图路径，可选。建议放在 <code>public/assets/</code>。</li>
            <li><code>pinned</code>: 是否置顶。</li>
            <li><code>draft</code>: 草稿。设为 <code>true</code> 时不会发布。</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="guide-card article-body">
          <h2>Callouts</h2>
          <p>文章里可以写 GitHub 风格提示框：</p>
          <pre><code>&gt; [!NOTE]
&gt; 普通说明。

&gt; [!TIP]
&gt; 小技巧。

&gt; [!WARNING]
&gt; 重要提醒。
</code></pre>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
